<template>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Enter a place">
</template>

<script>
    setup(){
        const input = ref(null);
        const autocomplete = ref(null);
        const place = ref(null);
        const ready = ref(false);
        const geolocation = ref(false);
        const manually = ref(false);
        const zoom = ref(15);
        const address = ref(null);
        const fallbackProcedure = ref(null);
        const getMapData = (data) => {
            place.value = data;
        };
        onMounted(() => {
            autocomplete.value = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(input.value);
            google.maps.event.addListener(autocomplete.value, 'place_changed', () => {
                place.value = autocomplete.value.getPlace();
            });
            ready.value = true;
        });
        return {
            input,
            autocomplete,
            place,
            ready,
            geolocation,
            manually,
            zoom,
            address,
            fallbackProcedure,
            getMapData
        };
    }
</script>

<style></style>
